                <div class="stat-label">Host Partners</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Trust & Safety</h3>
                <p>We prioritize the safety and security of our community with verified listings, secure payments, and reviews from real guests.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Authentic Experiences</h3>
                <p>We believe in travel that connects you to local cultures, traditions, and communities for truly memorable stays.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Community First</h3>
                <p>Our community of hosts and guests is at the heart of everything we do. We're here to support each other.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <p>We're a passionate team of travel enthusiasts, tech innovators, and customer service experts working together to revolutionize the vacation rental industry.</p>
