                <div class="team-name">Shivang Gupta</div>
                <div class="team-role">Founder & CEO</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Join Our Journey</h2>
        <p>Whether you're a traveler looking for your next adventure or a property owner wanting to share your space, HostHaven is here to make it happen. Join our growing community today and experience travel differently.</p>
    </div>
</div>
